{"tid":359532,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"連登原來仲有賣VIP卡","createTime":"2017-08-14T14:34:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-16T04:56:22.000Z","uid":134052,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3c8760ed435c7c4515b1d67c0805625b77cddb13","tid":359532,"uid":134052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T14:34:18.000Z","msg":"連尼住發達大計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之前推出會員卡<br />\n而家有埋VIP會員卡<br />\n我買咗中等等級張卡<br />\n當係資助下個server<br />\n希望唔好成日死<br />\n300蚊都幾貴下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但可以起埋用戶留言底<br />\n同埋一啲唔講得嘅功能<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/yW4fTpW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FyW4fTpW.jpg&h=1a36dc9c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n都唔錯嘅，但個包裝令人覺得似二手貨<br />\n最緊要都係後面個code啫"},{"pid":"d8d357eb5a0c451f7bd8a2b097ef02250448a65b","tid":359532,"uid":87229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T14:36:11.000Z","msg":"哇 屌 即刻落樓下買返3 4 5張叫埋喲fd一齊升vip先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n再唔買我驚又好似上次咁無哂貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a2cc80012471e27d741dc72340cf03b24e0d5ed","tid":359532,"uid":134052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T14:40:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>哇 屌 即刻落樓下買返3 4 5張叫埋喲fd一齊升vip先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n再唔買我驚又好似上次咁無哂貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我樓下啲7仔ok都冇晒白金，<br />\n得返啲鈦金以上<br />\n全部都500起跳<br />\n好貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ccfacdab52a11a4792981f596f7a93a973e9221","tid":359532,"uid":116530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T14:41:47.000Z","msg":"買邊張個名會變成金色？"},{"pid":"9aaf